  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Manager",
  "description": "<h2>Project Manager – Regional Digital Transformation (APAC)</h2><p>We are seeking a senior Project Manager to lead the end-to-end delivery of complex, large-scale digital transformation programs across <strong>Insurance, Aviation, Government, and Infrastructure</strong> sectors in the <strong>Asia-Pacific region</strong>.</p><p>This role requires a strong balance of <strong>technical delivery excellence, regional leadership, and executive stakeholder management</strong>, ensuring commercial success, regulatory compliance, and long-term client partnerships.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Lead end-to-end delivery of <strong>fixed-scope and large-scale Time & Materials (T&M) programs</strong>, managing teams of up to <strong>~200 FTEs</strong></p></li><li><p>Define, implement, and govern delivery frameworks including <strong>Agile, Scrum, V-Model, and hybrid methodologies</strong></p></li><li><p>Drive <strong>steering committee governance</strong>, executive reporting, and issue escalation</p></li><li><p>Own <strong>financial management</strong> including budgeting, forecasting, margin control, and cashflow</p></li><li><p>Lead <strong>contract negotiations</strong>, change requests, and SLA governance</p></li><li><p>Act as the <strong>primary client interface</strong> for regional and global clients based in Singapore</p></li><li><p>Provide leadership and mentorship to <strong>offshore delivery teams</strong>, primarily in Vietnam</p></li><li><p>Support <strong>pre-sales activities</strong>, solution shaping, and delivery estimations</p></li></ul><h3>Qualifications</h3><ul><li><p><strong>MBA</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Bachelor’s Degree in Computer Engineering</strong></p></li></ul><h3>Experience</h3><ul><li><p><strong>10+ years</strong> of experience in project, program, or delivery management</p></li><li><p>Proven track record managing <strong>large-scale T&M and fixed-price engagements</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong experience delivering transformation programs within <strong>regulated and enterprise environments</strong></p></li></ul><h3>Core Competencies</h3><ul><li><p>Program & Portfolio Management</p></li><li><p>Executive Client & Stakeholder Management</p></li><li><p>Financial & Commercial Governance</p></li><li><p>Offshore & Cross-Cultural Leadership</p></li><li><p>Risk, Compliance & Regulatory Management</p></li></ul>",
